-- Man Dies, 6 Hurt, 8 Missing After Boats Collide in Hong Kong, RTHK Says
-- B y   S t a n l e y   J a m e s
-- 2010-12-07T03:29:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-07/one-man-dies-8-people-missing-after-boats-collide-in-hong-kong-rthk-says.html
One man died and six people were
injured when a sand barge collided with a cargo vessel near Tung
Lung island in Hong Kong, Radio Television Hong Kong reported
today. Eight people are missing and an air and sea search
operation is under way, RTHK said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stanley James at 
 sjames8@bloomberg.net  